full_desc: If Q27ii. DSEPILEP (Epilepsy/seizure disorder)=0 (Condition not present), then UDS Form D1, Q22. EPILEP (Epilepsy (present)) should not equal 1 (Present)

short_desc: If DSEPILEP in (1-3), then EPILEP should not be blank or 0
full_desc: If Q27ii. DSEPILEP (Epilepsy/seizure disorder) is in 1-3 (recent conditon, condition in past 5 years, or lifelong condition), then UDS Form D1, Q22. EPILEP (Epilepsy (present)) should not be blank or 0 (No Epilepsy present)
test_logic: If DSEPILEP in (1-3) and (EPILEP is blank or EPILEP=0)

short_desc: If DSIMPVS=0, then VISION should not equal 0
full_desc: If Q27ff. DSIMPVS (Impaired vision)=0 (Condition not present), then UDS Form B1, Q5. VISION (Without corrective lenses, is vision functionally normal?) should not equal 0 (No, abnormal)

short_desc: If DSIMPVS in (1-3), VISION should not equal 1
full_desc: If Q27ff. DSIMPVS (Impaired vision) is in 1-3 (recent conditon, condition in past 5 years, or lifelong condition), then UDS Form B1, Q5. VISION (Without corrective lenses, is vision functionally normal?) should not equal 1 (Yes, normal)

short_desc: If DSIMPHR=0, then HEARING should not equal 0
full_desc: If Q27ee. DSIMPHR (Impaired hearing)=0 (Condition not present), then UDS Form B1, Q7. HEARING (Without a hearing aid(s) is hearing functionally normal?) should not equal 0 (No, abnormal)

short_desc: If DSIMPHR in (1-3), then HEARING should not equal 1
full_desc: If Q27ee. DSIMPHR (Impaired hearing) is in 1-3 (recent conditon, condition in past 5 years, or lifelong condition), then UDS Form B1, Q7. HEARING (Without a hearing aid(s) is hearing functionally normal?) should not equal 1 (Yes, normal)
